Maya Lin must have learned the virtues of honesty and integrity<br>
with herself and others at an early age.  It is my opinion<br>
that this is what gives her the gift of creative genius.<br>
From idea to the finished memorial, she showed grace and<br>
respect for those who opposed her submission.  To those who<br>
opposed her idea, I can respect that.  But one thing they<br>
can plainly see is here is one outstanding person in may<br>
ways.<br><br>
Make it simple. (quote: A. Einstien)
